713777f-a.title: Manhattan: 55th Street (West) - 10th Avenue
713777f-a.text:
West 55th Street, west from Tenth Ave., to the North (Hudson) River,
showing at the latter point Pier No. 95.
October 28, 1936.
W.P.A. Photo.
Federal Art Project.

713778f-a.title: Manhattan: 55th Street (West) - 10th Avenue
713778f-a.text:
West 55th Street, west from but not including Tenth Ave., to the North
(Hudson) River.
October 29, 1936.
W.P.A. Photo.
Federal Art Project.

713779f-a.title: Manhattan: 55th Street (West) - 10th Avenue
713779f-a.text:
West 55th Street, west from a point midway between Tenth and Eleventh Aves., to the North (Hudson) River, showing at the latter point Pier No. 95. Intersection shown in the foreground is Eleventh Ave.
October 28, 1936.
W.P.A. Photo.
Federal Art Project.
